ps://x.com/yoshibanakokoro" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>Kokoro Yoshihana</strong></a>和<a href="https://x.com/itopoid" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>Itopoid</strong></a> 。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/e420e8fab0c5aa2a49078d1b72f374d0-kix.vgewi5id23p2-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/e420e8fab0c5aa2a49078d1b72f374d0-kix.vgewi5id23p2-1024x576.webp" width="1024" height="576" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/e420e8fab0c5aa2a49078d1b72f374d0-kix.vgewi5id23p2-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/e420e8fab0c5aa2a49078d1b72f374d0-kix.vgewi5id23p2-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/e420e8fab0c5aa2a49078d1b72f374d0-kix.vgewi5id23p2-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/e420e8fab0c5aa2a49078d1b72f374d0-kix.vgewi5id23p2-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/e420e8fab0c5aa2a49078d1b72f374d0-kix.vgewi5id23p2-jpg.webp 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" ></a></p><p>在 Hakotore V 中，您可以通过将自己和 VTuber 叠加在镜面显示屏上来进行训练，从而轻松有趣地学习正确的姿势。此外，担任教练的VTuber的声音全部是新录制的。</p><p>此外，动作捕捉摄像头会检测玩家的动作，VTuber 会匹配玩家的节奏。菜单由热爱肌肉训练的VTuber和训练教练全程监督，设计涵盖了从初学者到资深用户、从有氧运动到高强度训练的所有内容。它还具有可以在SNS上发布的纪念照片功能，提供VTuber和粉丝在同一空间一起享受运动的体验。</p><h2>参与VTuber评论</h2><h3>初级课程教练：舞鹤洋加人</h3><p><a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/e420e8fab0c5aa2a49078d1b72f374d0-kix.29dfuukmalt-jpg.webp"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/e420e8fab0c5aa2a49078d1b72f374d0-kix.29dfuukmalt-300x300.webp" alt="" width="300" height="300" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-254021" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/e420e8fab0c5aa2a49078d1b72f374d0-kix.29dfuukmalt-300x300.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/e420e8fab0c5aa2a49078d1b72f374d0-kix.29dfuukmalt-150x150.webp 150w, h